{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "At the breakfast, which is 6:00",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "00 in the morning, we have no idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, I think, 5:00 in the morning and cool, because it was, you know, early May.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're serving us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First time in my life saw a big kettle like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the, the food was, I mean, disgusting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- actually, we knew after that what was it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Beets what you feed the cows with, big beets in big, thick slices, boiled-- and that's it, something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as we stay in line, who is beside the other side is one of my cousin from Olaszliszka, who all went a day before us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She already has a tiny little babushka covered her bare head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she's serving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when she sees me, she comes out of there, hugs me, says Evika, what you doing here?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, listen to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From this day on, you're 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from that day on-- she told me right away because she spoke pretty good German-- and taught me that you're 18 years old, [GERMAN] year old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how I register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they take the dates from then on, I was born in, you know, 1926, what, or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the date I gave them, obvious the right date, December 10.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother, just after liberation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no, nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- we have five cousin all the way through the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two of us came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, that day, we were only day, one day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From that day again, started to, you know, take us back to the, the train station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure it was a different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And put us in the cattle car, and ship us to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "P-L-S-Z-L-O-S-Z, Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
